songs.title: Ms. Professional
songs.lyrics:
[Hook]
You’re so professional
With yo 9 to 5, tryna make some revenue
Stand up five 'till five, looking straight incredible
But them guys be lying, really, they just scared of you
So girl I’m telling you
Well, give it to me right now, I could do you so
And we can do it right now, like we’re all alone
And I know you’re waiting to, do the things we’re made to do
What we’re made to do, we ain’t ashamed
So girl give it to me right now, you’re just like a pro

[Verse 1]
You know I am watching whenever you are on clock
I hope you never take a break I hope that you don’t stop
Imagination had me on the bottom, you on top
Every single time you break it down, you get ‘em
Every time you dress you’re blessed that is the best of death
I guess I’ll have to resurrect, they know you kill ‘em
Cooler than a cucumber, two thumbs up, put them up high
With high heels and you shoot on

[Hook]

[Bridge]
Yea, you’re doing it, doing it
You know just what to do with it, with that thang
You know you know just what to do with it, do with it
You know just what to do with it, with that thang
You know just what to do with that thing
You know I like the way you move with it, move with it
I like the way you move with it, with that thang
(You know) I like how you move with it, move with it
(You know) You're just like a pro (you know)

[Verse 2]
Ok, let me think, if I had a guess
I can tell by the way you type, I can tell by the way you dress
I can tell by the way you meet me, stacking papers across that desk
If you get down with a guy like me, you’ll be a veteran, you’ll be a vet
Light are off, now bring your waist to the edge of the bed
I heard your accident, you’re scratching and grabbing my neck
That is it, you know what I like
A business woman by day, foxy rentals by night

[Hook]

[Bridge]
I like the way you move with it (move with it)
I like the way you move with it, with that thang (with that thang)
I like the way you move with it, move with it, with that thang

[Hook]
So give it to me right now
I could use you so
And we can do it right now
Like we're all alone
And I know you’re waiting to
Do the things we’re made to do
What we’re made to do, we ain’t ashamed
So girl give it to me right now
You’re just like a pro
